OL,6,FSyed Hussain-Kazi, of Hardy Street in
OL,7,F, attacked 19-year-old University of
OL,8,FHull student Sachin Hawkins with a
OL,9,Fkitchen knife after an exchange of
OL,10,Finsults, heard.JHussain-Kazi, 25,
OL,11,Fdenied murdering Mr Hawkins on 15
OL,12,FNovember last year but was found
OL,13,Fguilty by a jury after a seven-day
OL,14,Ftrial.JThe court heard how violence
OL,15,Ferupted after Mr Hawkins began playing
OL,16,Fmusic in the kitchen of their shared
OL,17,Fhouse.
