OL,6,FHussain-Kazi, who had been helping to
OL,7,Ftidy up, started making fun of his
OL,8,Ftaste in music and the pair then
OL,9,Fexchanged insults. They usually called
OL,10,Feach other names, the court heard, but
OL,11,Fthe argument escalated.
