OL,6,FHussain-Kazi took exception to what he
OL,7,Fhad been called, asking: "What did you
OL,8,Fcall me?"JHe held Mr Hawkins against a
OL,9,Fwall and stabbed him in the chest with
OL,10,Fa kitchen knife, causing him to fall
OL,11,Fto the floor. Another person in the
OL,12,Fhouse then held Hussain-Kazi back.
OL,13,FHussain-Kazi said "I need to go",
OL,14,Fstepping over Mr Hawkins and saying
OL,15,F"I'm sorry" before leaving the house.
OL,17,FHe later told police that he did not
OL,18,Fintend to cause any harm to his
OL,19,Ffriend. The pair had met during their
OL,20,Ffirst year at university.
