OL,6,FMr Hawkins, an international student
OL,7,Ffrom the city of Freeport in the
OL,8,FUnited States, was taken to Hull Royal
OL,9,FInfirmary but died the same evening.
OL,10,FHe had ambitions to become a special
OL,11,Feducation teacher, the court heard.
OL,12,FDavid Lamb KC, mitigating, said it was
OL,13,Fa "tragic" case for the family of Mr
OL,14,FHawkins, but claimed Hussain-Kazi did
OL,15,Fnot intend to kill him.J"There was no
OL,16,Fplanning or premeditation sufficient
OL,17,Fto amount to an aggravating feature,"
OL,18,Fhe said. "Violence on this scale, if
OL,19,Fat all, was simply not contemplated.
OL,20,F"The violence was spontaneous and the
OL,21,Fdefendant did not search for, or
OL,22,Findeed, select a knife. Rather, it
OL,23,Fappears to have been, the evidence
OL,24,Fsuggests, close to (them)."JJudge John
OL,25,FThackray KC told Hussain-Kazi: "You
OL,26,Fthought nothing of the unending pain
